1. Rxh6! gxh6 2. Bxh6+ Ke7 (2... Nxh6 3. Rxh6 { and Black would be helpless. }) 3. Qh7+ Ke8 4. Qxg8+ Kd7 5. Qh7+ Qe7 6. Bf8 Qxh7 7. Rxh7+ Ke8 8. Rxa7 { and Black resigns. } 1-0


