or at least come near it. } 45... Ra1 { [%eval 0.83] } 46. Kd3 { [%eval 0.86] } { Had the King been at
e3 he could go to d4, which would have gained a very important
move. } 46... Kg7 { [%eval 0.77] } 47. b4?! { [%eval 0.0] } { Inaccuracy. Kd4 was best. } (47. Kd4 f5) 47... Rf1 { [%eval 0.0] } { Best. Black, however, would have
accomplished nothing with this move, had the white King been
at d4. } 48. Ke3 { [%eval 0.0] } { The remainder of the game needs no comments. } 48... Rb1 { [%eval 0.0] } 49. Rc6 { [%eval 0.0] } 49... Rxb4 { [%eval 0.0] } 50. Rxa6 { [%eval 0.0] } 50... Rb2 { [%eval 0.0] } { 1/2-1/2 The game is a draw. } 1/2-1/2


