3 { [%eval 0.53] } 18... e5 { [%eval 0.58] } 19. Nxd7?! { [%eval -0.1] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was Qg3. } { (0.91 → 0.00) Inaccuracy. Best move was a3. } { SF DOESN'T LIKE TRADING THE GOOD N FOR THE LOCKED IN B. } (19. a3) (19. Qg3 Bf5 20. a3 Rf7 21. Re2 Bg6 22. b4 axb4 23. cxb4 Re7 24. Rae1 Rbe8 25. h3 Bh5) 19... e4?? { [%eval 7.77] } { (0.00 → 7.80) Blunder. Best move was Qxd7. } (19... Qxd7 20. dxe5 fxe5 21. Qg3 e4 22. Rad1 Qf5 23. Qe3 a4 24. bxa4 Ra8 25. c4 dxc4 26. Re2) 20. Qh3 { [%eval 7.61] } 20... Rf7 { [%eval 8.17] } 21. Nc5?! { [%eval 5.01] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was Nxb8. } { (8.11 → 5.07) Inaccuracy. Best move was Nxb8. } { Ran into major time-trouble and no longer thinking clearly? } { Nope, not time trouble. Just speed-induced blindness. I had 3 min left and he had almost 4.
