[UTCTime "13:16:47"]

44. Rxh3 { White gives me my opportunity on his very next move as he blunders 44. Rxh3! Though still at a significant disadvantage, that was all I needed to start pecking at his advantage until I equalized and he accepted my offer to call it a draw. } 44... Rxe5+ 45. Kd4 Re6 46. Rh5 { Well, perhaps this move was also required... } 46... Kxd6 47. Rd5+ Kc6 48. Rc5+ Kb6 49. b4 Rh6 50. Kc4 Rh4+ 51. Kb3 Rh1 52. Ka2 Rh4 53. Kb3 Rh1 54. Kc2 Rh4 55. Kc3 { Players agree on a draw. } *


